legs.start_address: Çarşı, Bahriye Üçok Cd. No:1, 08000 Artvin Merkez/Artvin, Turkey

steps.html_instructions: Head northwest on Bahriye Üçok Cd. toward Cumhuriyet Cd.
Miralay Şükrü Bey Cd. turns slightly left and becomes Zeytin Sk.

At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto Erzurum Artvin Yolu/D950
Continue to follow D950

Take the ramp onto Kars-Erzincan Yolu/D100
Continue to follow D100

Turn left onto Cumhuriyet Cd./Tutak Karayazı Yolu/D270
Continue to follow Tutak Karayazı Yolu/D270
At the roundabout, take the 3rd exit onto Atatürk Blv.
Emniyet Cd. turns slightly right and becomes Van Blv.

Continue straight onto Erciş Van Yolu/D975
Continue to follow D975

Turn left onto Şabaniye Cd./D975
Continue to follow D975

At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto Hakkari Yolu/D975
Continue to follow D975

Turn left onto Van Hakkari Yolu/D975
Continue to follow D975
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto Hakkari-Van Blv.

Continue onto İstiklall Cd.
Destination will be on the right
